reviewText: best rock group on dvd thats great
I love how this band has so much energy on stage, especially the vocalist, Johnny Gioeli. Great for Axel Rudi Pell fans!
The audio CD was Fantastic..The Dvd is not that good though,the lighting is so bright it's hard to make out the players themselfs ,could have been much better,bootleg quality!!

I have not even watched this dvd set yet but I am so confident in ARP since all their other dvds have kicked ass!  Almost no one of them has heard of them here in Oklahoma.  I wonder if Mike Terrana ever takes a breather as he seems to be busy with Tarja too!
